metadata.name: Madame et sa caniche
metadata.description:
Bitches is a series of digital paintings inspired by dogs and the fabulous people that love them.

Connect with Monty on [Twitter](https://twitter.com/_MontyPreston) if you're interested in a commission.

See more of Monty's dog-inspired artworks [on OpenSea](https://opensea.io/collection/dogs-of-discord).
